It seems like everyone now has a Voice Mailbox. Why these are so popular I
don't know.

Along with these Voice Mailboxes are a number of infolines full of codes and
other information. I've even seen a few on-line infolines. They're usually
full of information so if you see one posted somewhere, you might consider
calling it.

