New Editorship at Phrack!
<><><><><><><><><><><><><>


Phrack Inc. Has had a number of major changes in editorship. According to
Phrack 15:


"Phrack Inc. is now in the hands of Sir Francis Drake, Elric Of Imrryr, and Shooting Shark."


The above statement was from Knight Lightning. With Taran King and Knight
Lightning in college, control of Phrack is in the hands of SFD, Elric Of
Imrryr, and Shooting Shark. These new editors are not new to the hacking
world and I'm sure most phreaks/hackers in the modem world are familiar with
their handles.

The new editors of Phrack have released two issues so far. The issues are
#15 and #16 and contain the following files:



Phrack 15 Table of Contents
===========================


15-1.   Phrack XV Intro by Shooting Shark                (2K)
15-2.   More Stupid Unix Tricks by Shooting Shark        (10K)
15-3.   Making Free Local Payfone Calls by Killer Smurf  (7K)
15-4.   Advanced Carding XIV by The Disk Jockey          (12K)
15-5.   Gelled Flame Fuels by Elric of Imrryr            (12K)
15-6.   PWN I:   The Busts by Knight Lightning           (xK)
15-7.   PWN II:  The Scoop on Dan The Operator by KL     (xK)
15-8.   PWN III: The Affidavit by SFD                    (6K)



Phrack 16 Table of Contents
===========================


Phrack 16 Intro by Elric of Imrryr                        2K
BELLCORE Information by The Mad Phone-Man                11K
A Hacker's Guide to Primos: Part 1 by Cosmos Kid         11K
Hacking GTN by The Kurgan                                 7K
Credit Card Laws Laws by Tom Brokow                       7K
Tapping Telephone Lines by Agent Steal                    9K
Reading Trans-Union Credit Reports by The Disk Jockey     6K

Phrack World News:

The Story Of the West German Hackers by Shooting Shark    3K
The Mad Phone-Man and the Gestapo by The Mad Phone-Man    2K
Flight of the Mad Phone-Man by The Mad Phone-Man          2K
Shadow Hack Busted Again by Shooting Shark                2K
Coin Box Thief Wanted by The $muggler                     2K



According to Phrack 16, submissions for Phrack can be sent to the following
bulletin boards:

Unlimited Reality       313-489-0747 Phrack
The Free World          301-668-7657 Phrack Inc. (*)
The Executive Inn       915-581-5145 Phrack
Lunatic Labs UnLtd.     415-278-7421 Phrack      (*)
House of the Rising Sun 401-789-1809 Phrack


* You will get the quickest repstems.


